snippet.title: Java Arrays Tutorial
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast
- This Java arrays tutorial will get your code working quickly! In this java tutorial, I show you how to use arrays in java. 

Java arrays can be a little tricky if you're new to programming, but fear not! They aren't too bad :) If you followed along, congrats! You learned-by-doing!

Source Code: https://github.com/alexlorenlee/JavaTutorialCode/blob/master/Arrays/ZombieKiller.java

I hope you enjoyed this java arrays tutorial! I like to have a nice mix of tutorials and actual projects for you all :)

Do you want to learn how to code from scratch, in Java? Check out my Java Tutorial For Beginners: https://youtu.be/woJb2hAfkO0

How'd you customize your zombie killer array?
